ReadCase1
data.value: select distinct top(1) T1.CLOSURE_REASON, T1.NUMB, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP from CKT_CASE T1 join CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 on (T1.NUMB = T2.CAS_NUMBER) and (T2.TYPE in ('AP', 'AR')) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T1.CLOSURE_REASON in (' ', 'NL')) join CKT_CSE_PERSON_ACC T4 on (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER) and (T4.TYPE = @type) order by T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP

data.name: ReadCase2
data.value: select distinct T1.CLOSURE_REASON, T1.NUMB, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP from CKT_CASE T1 join CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 on (T1.NUMB = T2.CAS_NUMBER) and (T2.TYPE in ('AP', 'AR')) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T1.CLOSURE_REASON = ' ') join CKT_CSE_PERSON_ACC T4 on (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER) and (T4.TYPE = @type) order by T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP

data.name: ReadCase3
data.value: select distinct T1.CLOSURE_REASON, T1.NUMB, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP from CKT_CASE T1 join CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 on (T1.NUMB = T2.CAS_NUMBER) and (T2.TYPE in ('AP', 'AR')) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T1.CLOSURE_REASON in (' ', 'NL')) order by T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP

data.name: ReadCase4
data.value: select distinct T1.CLOSURE_REASON, T1.NUMB, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP from CKT_CASE T1 join CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 on (T1.NUMB = T2.CAS_NUMBER) and (T2.TYPE in ('AP', 'AR')) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) order by T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP

data.name: ReadCashReceiptDetail
data.value: select top(1) CRV_IDENTIFIER, CST_IDENTIFIER, CRT_IDENTIFIER, CRD_ID, INTERFACE_TRAN_ID, ADJUSTMENT_IND, COURT_ORDER_NUMBER, CASE_NUMBER, OFFSET_TAXID, RECEIVED_AMOUNT, COLLECTION_AMOUNT, COLLECTION_DATE, MULTI_PAYOR, OFFSET_TAX_YEAR, JOINT_RETURN_IND, JOINT_RETURN_NAME, DFLTD_COLL_DAT_IND, OBLGOR_PRSN_NBR, OBLGOR_SSN, OBLGOR_FIRST_NM, OBLGOR_LAST_NM, OBLGOR_MID_NM, OBLGOR_PHONE_NBR, PAYEE_FIRST_NAME, PAYEE_MIDDLE_NAME, PAYEE_LAST_NAME, SUP_PRSN_FRST_NM1, SUP_PRSN_MID_NM1, SUP_PRSN_LST_NM1, SUP_PRSN_FRST_NM2, SUP_PRSN_LST_NM2, SUP_PRSN_MID_NM2, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, REFUNDED_AMT, DISTRIBUTED_AMT, COLLAMT_APPL_IND, SUPP_PERS_NO_VOL, REFERENC, NOTES, OVRRD_MNL_DIST_IND from CKT_CR_DETAIL where (CRD_ID = @crdId) and (CRV_IDENTIFIER = @crvIdentifier) and (CST_IDENTIFIER = @cstIdentifier) and (CRT_IDENTIFIER = @crtIdentifier)

data.name: ReadCashReceiptDetailStatHistoryCashReceiptDetailStatus
data.value: select top(1) T1.CRD_IDENTIFIER, T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER, T1.CST_IDENTIFIER, T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER, T1.CDS_IDENTIFIER, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.REASON_CODE_ID, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.REASON_TEXT, T2.CODE, T2.NAME from CKT_CR_DETAIL_STAT T2 join CKT_CRDTL_STATHIST T1 on (@crdIdentifier = T1.CRD_IDENTIFIER) and (@crvIdentifier = T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER) and (@cstIdentifier = T1.CST_IDENTIFIER) and (@crtIdentifier = T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CRDETAIL_STAT_ID = T1.CDS_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE = @discontinueDate) order by T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadCashReceiptDetailStatus
data.value: select top(1) CRDETAIL_STAT_ID, CODE, NAME from CKT_CR_DETAIL_STAT where CRDETAIL_STAT_ID = @crdetailStatId

data.name: ReadCashReceiptEventCashReceiptTypeCashReceiptSourceType
data.value: select top(1) T1.CST_IDENTIFIER, T1.CREVENT_ID, T1.RECEIVED_DATE, T2.CRTYPE_ID, T2.CODE, T2.NAME, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T3.INTERFACE_IND, T3.CODE, T3.NAME from CKT_CR_TYPE T2, CKT_CRSRC_TYPE T3 join CKT_CR_EVENT T1 on (T1.CREVENT_ID = @creventId) and (T1.CST_IDENTIFIER = @cstIdentifier) and (T3.CR_SRCE_TYPE_ID = T1.CST_IDENTIFIER) where T2.CRTYPE_ID = @crtypeId

data.name: ReadCsePersonAddress
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, CSP_NUMBER, SEND_DATE, SOURCE, STREET_1, STREET_2, CITY, TYPE, WORKER_ID, VERIFIED_DATE, END_DATE, END_CODE, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CREATED_BY, [STATE], ZIP_CODE, ZIP4, ZIP3, STREET_3, STREET_4, PROVINCE, POSTAL_CODE, COUNTRY, LOCATION_TYPE from CKT_CSE_PERS_ADDR where (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (VERIFIED_DATE <= @verifiedDate) and (END_DATE > @verifiedDate) and (TYPE = 'M') order by VERIFIED_DATE desc

data.name: ReadInterstatePaymentAddress
data.value: select INT_GENERATED_ID, ADDRESS_START_DATE, TYPE, STREET1, STREET2, CITY, ZIP_5, ADDRESS_END_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TIMES, PAYABLE_TO_NAME, [STATE], ZIP_CODE, ZIP4, ZIP3, COUNTY, LOCATION_TYPE, FIPS_COUNTY, FIPS_STATE, FIPS_LOCATION, ROUTING_NUMBER_ABA, ACCOUNT_NUMBER_DFI, ACCOUNT_TYPE from CKT_INT_PYMNT_ADDR where (@intGeneratedId = INT_GENERATED_ID) and (ADDRESS_END_DATE > @addressEndDate)

data.name: ReadInterstateRequest
data.value: select top(1) T1.IDENTIFIER from CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST T1 join CKT_DISB_TRAN T2 on (T1.IDENTIFIER = T2.INT_INTER_ID) and (@prqGeneratedId = T2.PRQ_GENERATED_ID)

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest1
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, PROCESS_DATE, AMOUNT, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, DP_CSE_PER_NUM, CSE_PERSON_NUMBER, IMPREST_FUND_CODE, CLASSIFICATION, NUMBER, PRINT_DATE, TYPE, RCT_R_TSTAMP, PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID, INTERSTATE_IND, RECOUPMENT_IND_KPC from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST where NUMBER = @number

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest2
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, PROCESS_DATE, AMOUNT, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, DP_CSE_PER_NUM, CSE_PERSON_NUMBER, IMPREST_FUND_CODE, CLASSIFICATION, NUMBER, PRINT_DATE, TYPE, RCT_R_TSTAMP, PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID, INTERSTATE_IND, RECOUPMENT_IND_KPC from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST where PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = @paymentRequestId

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest3
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, PROCESS_DATE, AMOUNT, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, DP_CSE_PER_NUM, CSE_PERSON_NUMBER, IMPREST_FUND_CODE, CLASSIFICATION, NUMBER, PRINT_DATE, TYPE, RCT_R_TSTAMP, PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID, INTERSTATE_IND, RECOUPMENT_IND_KPC from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST where PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = @paymentRequestId

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest4
data.value: select top(1) count(*) from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST where NUMBER = @number

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest5
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, NUMBER, TYPE, PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST where @prqRGeneratedId = PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest6
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, NUMBER, TYPE, RCT_R_TSTAMP, PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST where NUMBER = @number

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest7
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, PROCESS_DATE, AMOUNT, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, DP_CSE_PER_NUM, CSE_PERSON_NUMBER, IMPREST_FUND_CODE, CLASSIFICATION, NUMBER, PRINT_DATE, TYPE, PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST where NUMBER = @number

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest8
data.value: select top(1) T1.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, T1.NUMBER, T1.TYPE, T1.RCT_R_TSTAMP, T1.PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST T1 join CKT_PMNT_REQUEST T2 on (T1.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = T2.PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = @paymentRequestId)

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest9
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID, INTERSTATE_IND from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST where PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = @paymentRequestId

data.name: ReadPaymentStatus1
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_STATUS_ID, CODE, NAME, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATE_BY, LAST_UPDATE_TMST, DESCRIPTION from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS where PAYMENT_STATUS_ID = @paymentStatusId

data.name: ReadPaymentStatus2
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_STATUS_ID, CODE from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS where CODE = 'CAN'

data.name: ReadPaymentStatus3
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_STATUS_ID, CODE, LAST_UPDATE_BY from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS where CODE = @code

data.name: ReadPaymentStatus4
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_STATUS_ID, CODE from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS where CODE = 'KPC'

data.name: ReadPaymentStatus5
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_STATUS_ID, CODE from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS where CODE = @code

data.name: ReadPaymentStatus6
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_STATUS_ID, CODE from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS where CODE = 'PAID'

data.name: ReadPaymentStatus7
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_STATUS_ID, CODE from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS where CODE = 'REQ'

data.name: ReadPaymentStatusHistory1
data.value: select top(1) PST_GENERATED_ID, PRQ_GENERATED_ID, PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, REASON_TEXT from CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST where (PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID = @pymntStatHistId) and (@prqGeneratedId = PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (@pstGeneratedId = PST_GENERATED_ID)

data.name: ReadPaymentStatusHistory2
data.value: select distinct top(1) T1.PST_GENERATED_ID, T1.PRQ_GENERATED_ID, T1.PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.REASON_TEXT from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS T3 join CKT_PMNT_REQUEST T2 join CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST T1 on (T2.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = T1.PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.NUMBER = @number) on (T3.PAYMENT_STATUS_ID = T1.PST_GENERATED_ID) and (T3.CODE = 'REML') order by T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadPaymentStatusHistory3
data.value: select distinct top(1) T1.PST_GENERATED_ID, T1.PRQ_GENERATED_ID, T1.PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.REASON_TEXT from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS T2 join CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST T1 on (@prqGeneratedId = T1.PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.PAYMENT_STATUS_ID = T1.PST_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.CODE = 'REML') order by T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadPaymentStatusHistory4
data.value: select PST_GENERATED_ID, PRQ_GENERATED_ID, PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, REASON_TEXT from CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST where (@prqGeneratedId = PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (CREATED_TIMESTAMP < @createdTimestamp) order by CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadPaymentStatusHistory5
data.value: select PST_GENERATED_ID, PRQ_GENERATED_ID, PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, REASON_TEXT from CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST where (DISCONTINUE_DATE = @discontinueDate) and (@prqGeneratedId = PRQ_GENERATED_ID) order by CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadPaymentStatusPaymentStatusHistory
data.value: select top(1) T1.PAYMENT_STATUS_ID, T1.CODE, T1.NAME, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.LAST_UPDATE_BY, T1.LAST_UPDATE_TMST, T1.DESCRIPTION, T2.PRQ_GENERATED_ID, T2.PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.CREATED_BY, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.REASON_TEXT from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS T1 join CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST T2 on (@prqGeneratedId = T2.PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.PAYMENT_STATUS_ID = T2.PST_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE = @discontinueDate)

data.name: ReadProgram
data.value: select distinct T1.PROGRAM_ID, T1.CODE from CKT_PROGRAM T1 join CKT_PERSON_PROGRAM T2 on (T1.PROGRAM_ID = T2.PRG_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber)

data.name: ReadReceiptRefund1
data.value: select top(1) CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CRV_IDENTIFIER, CRD_IDENTIFIER, CRT_IDENTIFIER, CST_IDENTIFIER from CKT_RECEIPT_REFUND where CREATED_TIMESTAMP = @createdTimestamp

data.name: ReadReceiptRefund2
data.value: select top(1) CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CRV_IDENTIFIER, CRD_IDENTIFIER, CRT_IDENTIFIER, CST_IDENTIFIER from CKT_RECEIPT_REFUND where CREATED_TIMESTAMP = @createdTimestamp

data.name: ReadWarrantRemailAddress1
data.value: select top(1) WARRANT_REMAIL_ID, STREET_1, STREET_2, CITY, [STATE], ZIP_CODE_4, ZIP_CODE_5, ZIP_CODE_3, NAME, REMAIL_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, PRQ_ID from CKT_WRNT_RML_ADDR where @prqId = PRQ_ID order by CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadWarrantRemailAddress2
data.value: select top(1) WARRANT_REMAIL_ID, STREET_1, STREET_2, CITY, [STATE], ZIP_CODE_4, ZIP_CODE_5, ZIP_CODE_3, NAME, REMAIL_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, PRQ_ID from CKT_WRNT_RML_ADDR where @prqId = PRQ_ID order by CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: UpdateCashReceiptDetail
data.value: update CKT_CR_DETAIL set LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, LAST_UPDATED_TMST = @lastUpdatedTmst, REFUNDED_AMT = @refundedAmt, COLLAMT_APPL_IND = @collamtApplInd where (CRV_IDENTIFIER = @crvIdentifier) and (CST_IDENTIFIER = @cstIdentifier) and (CRT_IDENTIFIER = @crtIdentifier) and (CRD_ID = @crdId)

data.name: UpdateCashReceiptDetailStatHistory
data.value: update CKT_CRDTL_STATHIST set DISCONTINUE_DATE = @discontinueDate where (CRD_IDENTIFIER = @crdIdentifier) and (CRV_IDENTIFIER = @crvIdentifier) and (CST_IDENTIFIER = @cstIdentifier) and (CRT_IDENTIFIER = @crtIdentifier) and (CDS_IDENTIFIER = @cdsIdentifier) and (CREATED_TIMESTAMP = @createdTimestamp)

data.name: UpdateInterstatePaymentAddress
data.value: update CKT_INT_PYMNT_ADDR set STREET1 = @street1, STREET2 = @street2, CITY = @city, ZIP_5 = @zip5, LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, LAST_UPDATED_TIMES = @lastUpdatedTimes, PAYABLE_TO_NAME = @payableToName, [STATE] = @state, ZIP_CODE = @zipCode, ZIP4 = @zip4, ZIP3 = @zip3 where (INT_GENERATED_ID = @intGeneratedId) and (ADDRESS_START_DATE = @addressStartDate)

data.name: UpdatePaymentRequest1
data.value: update CKT_PMNT_REQUEST set RECOUPMENT_IND_KPC = @recoupmentIndKpc where PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = @paymentRequestId

data.name: UpdatePaymentRequest2
data.value: update CKT_PMNT_REQUEST set PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID = null where PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = @paymentRequestId

data.name: UpdatePaymentStatusHistory1
data.value: update CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST set DISCONTINUE_DATE = @discontinueDate where (PST_GENERATED_ID = @pstGeneratedId) and (PRQ_GENERATED_ID = @prqGeneratedId) and (PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID = @pymntStatHistId)

data.name: UpdatePaymentStatusHistory2
data.value: update CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST set REASON_TEXT = @reasonText where (PST_GENERATED_ID = @pstGeneratedId) and (PRQ_GENERATED_ID = @prqGeneratedId) and (PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID = @pymntStatHistId)
